Developer Terms of Use
des:
Whether you’re expecting a baby or you’re a new mom or dad, we know you’ve got lots of questions. In addition to consultations with your healthcare team, The Stork Report from Ochsner Health delivers daily advice on how to navigate parenthood. Tips range from how best to position your bed pillows to travel suggestions to breastfeeding.

DISCLAIMER: The information provided in this skill is for informational and educational purposes only, and is not a substitute for professional medical advice, treatment or diagnosis. Call your doctor to receive medical advice. If you think you may have a medical emergency, please dial 911.
